title: C.D. Veracruz (women)
text:
Club Tiburones Femenil was a Mexican women's <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Veracruz%20City">Veracruz City</a>, <a href="Veracruz">Veracruz</a>, <a href="Mexico">Mexico</a>. The club was the female section of <a href="Tiburones%20Rojos%20de%20Veracruz">Tiburones Rojos de Veracruz</a> between 2017 and 2019. The team played in the <a href="Liga%20MX%20Femenil">Liga MX Femenil</a> which started in July 2017.
